PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Consumer and Corporate Affairs of John M. Weekes, of Ottawa, Ontario, as a member of the Standards Council of Canada to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of John Anthony Gilbert, whose term has expired.
